{"tid":1281885,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"突發 polyu校長回應71事件","createTime":"2019-07-03T11:56:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T02:24:00.000Z","uid":40867,"like":6,"dislike":137,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"181371d49e57568210f72930755e709d28ecb7c3","tid":1281885,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:56:09.000Z","msg":"各位同事、各位同學： <br />\n<br />\n對於七月一日立法會大樓的衝擊事件，我和你們一樣深感痛心。我們一方面十分明白社會上的情緒，另一方面也非常關注同學的安全和福祉。 <br />\n<br />\n無論在任何情況下，暴力始終不是解決問題的方法。法治是香港的核心價值之一，也是香港數十年來賴以成功的基石。我們希望本著共同的目標，令香港繼續成為一個多元自由、寬容和平的社會，冀盼各方即使持不同意見，仍能在互相尊重的基礎上，以冷靜、理性及和平的方式建立具建設性的對話，以化解當前的矛盾。 <br />\n<br />\n校長 <br />\n滕錦光 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nDear Colleagues and Students <br />\n<br />\nLike many of you, I am deeply saddened by the storming of the Legislative Council Complex on 1 July. While we are fully aware of the sentiments in our society, we are very concerned about the wellness and well-being of our students. <br />\n<br />\nIn any situation, violence can never be a means to resolve problems. Hong Kong&rsquo;s greatest strength &ndash; the rule of law &ndash; is one of its core values and the cornerstone of its success for decades. Sharing a common goal that Hong Kong will continue to be a pluralistic, free, accommodating and peaceful community, we hope people with different views yet on the ground of mutual respect, would build constructive conversations in a calm, rational and peaceful manner to resolve the current divisions. <br />\n<br />\nBest regards <br />\n<br />\nJin-Guang Teng <br />\nPresident <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4da1b9075de9c5eaaa176db327bbf2dcd11138cb","tid":1281885,"uid":40867,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:56:48.000Z","msg":"食屎啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6c1262e84b28e671b367b96e6d81ec6f2311150","tid":1281885,"uid":157391,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:57:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4772ae1096568c256e6301420edb2d10727c3e4","tid":1281885,"uid":40867,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:57:58.000Z","msg":"法治是香港的核心價值之一，也是香港數十年來賴以成功的基石。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇到都嬲<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e7319eec4d8e11083be045e239ab4d4e5a74ee5","tid":1281885,"uid":27670,"like":34,"dislike":2,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:58:32.000Z","msg":"見到個名pinyin已經唔駛睇<img sr