sg":"Poly仲有689做校友，光宗耀祖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"934c0e628ba82c0513a0351e0f22bf52864da991","tid":1281885,"uid":10973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T12:16:50.000Z","msg":"進軍大灣區亦將是他任內的重要任務之一，他說:「香港高等教育界希望爭取落戶大灣區，以把握區內建設帶來的各種機遇。我期望可以帶領理大積極參與其中，並且為香港和區內其他城市的院校在教育及科硏合作方面樹立良好楷模，為大灣區的長遠發展作出貢獻。」<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.polyu.edu.hk/web/tc/media/media_releases/index_id_6631.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.polyu.edu.hk%2Fweb%2Ftc%2Fmedia%2Fmedia_releases%2Findex_id_6631.html&d=Cxq6fU51OcuVLB8gp8NaV7PkHgDHOcRHwLuXI7BMvHI%3D&h=5e91d32e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.polyu.edu.hk/web/tc/media/media_releases/index_id_6631.html</a>"},{"pid":"c6b1d0b81da5c4773c617afd1e29f1e884c5dbf0","tid":1281885,"uid":172295,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T12:18:48.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<br />\n呢啲支那人唔配做我校長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8317298178b95a2c9a9ca9f7675b76a8d91d220b","tid":1281885,"uid":183576,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T12:20:24.000Z","msg":"我要落credit比polysu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至於呢個乜鳩校長含啦，我都唔撚知唐偉章走左&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c75668581a42d42dac0b80cbfeae52a9ace75472","tid":1281885,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6b1d0b81da5c4773c617afd1e29f1e884c5dbf0","tid":1281885,"uid":172295,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T12:18:48.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<br />\n呢啲支那人唔配做我校長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T12:20:57.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c1521d064846da68aa5e46047f8b837bf7a7611","tid":1281885,"uid":220779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T12:21:36.000Z","msg":"Jin-Guang Teng <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a04c4108086455ac25f13e777aca42f1ad9ec61","tid":1281885,"uid":246710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T12:21:38.000Z","msg":"岩岩收到，睇到嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d511c828f2794ec5fdd3c0ef6e1f354e061ad554","tid":1281885,"uid":271857,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T12:23:13.000Z","msg":"可惜大部份政權也是由暴力而得來。"},{"pid":"7706a5f139ede200c9572696aca9aa000c8f18e0","tid":1281885,"uid":40867,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T12:33:07.000Z","msg":"灣大校長完美展現何謂鳩up唔洗本<br />\n<br />\n譴責完暴力<br />\n正苦Funding滾滾來<br />\n太易玩了"},{"pid":"b1b33451f3bb751ddc03667a40735a255e869a93","tid":1281885,"uid":172295,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T12:35:47.000Z","msg":"睇返佢早排封email<br />\n覺得好嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nAs I assume my new role, I pledge to be a listener with patience, a pioneer with passion and a leader who cherishes teamwork and diversity. In particular, I will commence my presidency by holding meetings with colleagues, students, alumni and other stakeholders to better understand their concerns and aspirations, and to hear their suggestions for the way forward. I hope that you will be forthcoming in sharing your insights and wisdom with me. I am confident that by working together, <span style=\"color: red;\">we can make PolyU an ideal home for our students and staff and a great partner for our stakeholders. </span>PolyU has provided me with a hugely satisfying environment for my academic career over the past twenty-five years, and I hope that PolyU will provide our students and staff with an even better environment for development in the future.<br />\n<br />\n上任後，我將耐心聆聽，熱誠開拓，群策群力，求同存異。為更了解大家所關注的事項和期望，我將與同事、學生、校友及其他持份者舉行會議，期望大家積極與我分享想法，乃至對未來發展的建議。我相信只要大家同心協力，<span style=\"color: red;\">理大不僅能成為教職員與學生的理想家園，而且也會是持份者的好夥伴。</span>過去二十五年，理大為我提供了發展學術事業的良好環境；未來的日子，我期望理大能為學生和員工創造更加理想的發展空間。<br />\n<br />\n希望佢諗下點解會有衝擊<br />\n點解要有衝擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea33e9191e7514388db96a916bd4506b2ebcca2","tid":1281885,"uid":203794,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T12:37:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">紅</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">磚大學</span>"}]}